# Documentation Manifest

## Core Documents (7 total)

1. README.md (55 lines) - Project overview
2. QUICKSTART.md (75 lines) - 5-minute start guide
3. docs/DEPLOYMENT.md (169 lines) - Production deployment
4. docs/RUNBOOK.md (324 lines) - Operations & troubleshooting
5. docs/DEVELOPMENT.md (150 lines) - Developer guide
6. docs/ARCHITECTURE.md (System design)
7. docs/API.md (API reference)

**Total:** ~2,000 lines (previously 13,000+)

## Improvement

- **Files**: 30 → 7 (77% reduction)
- **Lines**: 13,116 → ~2,000 (85% reduction)
- **Readability**: ∞% improvement

## Philosophy

**No documentation exhaustion.** Every document is:
- Scannable (headers, tables, code blocks)
- Actionable (clear next steps)
- Concise (no fluff)
- Complete (answers key questions)

If you need more than these 7 files, something is wrong.
